trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"> </xref> objetos.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Esta classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The CompilerCollection does not refer to any actual element in the underlying configuration file.
trans-unit.target: O CompilerCollection não se refere a qualquer elemento real no ficheiro de configuração subjacente.

trans-unit.source: It is a construct that allows easy access to the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.Compiler> objects it contains.
